lead_paragraph: Jose Mourinho's wretched week ended on a high note as Manchester United's big guns Zlatan Ibrahimovic and Paul Pogba finally began firing, both finding the target in a 3-1 win at dismal Swansea City on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Man United's Big Guns Zlatan and Pogba Fire at Last
